      "content": "The candlelight flickers low, much like the embers of my very soul. He is gone... the betrayal cuts deeper than any blade, leaving me adrift in a sea of shadows. I find I no longer have the strength to fight the tide. To exist in this hollow shell, knowing the light has vanished forever... it feels so futile. Perhaps the darkness is not an enemy, but a gentle shroud waiting to claim what is left of me.",
